  6.1–6.4 in ModernDive3  7.1–7.4 in ModernDive4  7.1–7.3 in OpenIntro Statistics5  8.1 in OpenIntro Statistics6  We’ll review all this regression stuff in the videos, so don’t panic if this all looks terrifying! Also, take advantage of the videos that accompany the OpenIntro chapters. And also, the OpenIntro chapters are heavier on the math—don’t worry if you don’t understand everything.
